                    "body": "When you want to use 2 validators of the same type you must simply create and use 2 validators with different options.\r\n\r\nHow translation is processed has no effect of the validators usage.\r\nIn your case you would have the same problem when you use messages instead of keys.\r\nThis is the reason why your peoposed change will not be added.\r\n\r\nFor details you should give an reproduceable example of your problem.\r\nOtherwise this issue will be closed as wont fix.\r\n",
